dcterms:description: PACS is a generalization benchmark dataset in the image classification domain, which contains four fields: art paintings, cartoons, photos, and sketches. Each domain contains 7 categories of images, totaling 9,991 images, with an image size of 224 Ã— 224 pixels. This dataset has large stylistic differences between domains and is more challenging.

dcterms:description: The Diverse-Weather Dataset is built for urban-scene detection domain generalization, containing five domains with different weather conditions: Daytime Clear, Night Clear, Dusk Rainy, Night Rainy, and Daytime Foggy. The Daytime Clear domain consists of 19,395 training images, and 8,313 images are used as the validation set.
dcterms:title: Diverse-Weather Dataset
